After a tearful Tim Allen, the star, told a joke for a cast and
crew drenched in tears, they taped a slightly maudlin story,
scheduled to be broadcast on May 25, in which Allen's character
reaffirms his love for his wife and family, and his loyal sidekick
finds the love that had long eluded him, lending the closing a
poignant moral gravity. The episode is touching, and a historical
relic, as the traditional family sitcom goes the way of the
western. By James Sterngold.
