 c.1999 Fairchild Publications  
<TEXT>
 &UR; (Distributed by New York Times Special Features) &LR;  &QC;
<P>
   Who are the most-desired and inspiring men in the fields of
sports, entertainment, politics and the arts? See if you agree with
the coveted picks below:
</P>
<P>
   &UR; TELEVISION: DYLAN McDERMOTT &LR;  &QL;
