<SLUG> BC-MONTINI-COLUMN-AZR </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
IS TEEN BOY A THREAT OR A VICTIM? 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By E.J. MONTINI  
 c.1999 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
<P>
   PHOENIX - Days before the massacre at Columbine High School in
