to benefit all the children, including the child who may have used
poor judgment. &QL; 
THE FEAR EQUATION
</P>
<P>
   &QL;
</P>
<P>
   He said the suspension hearing ``is to make sure we have all the
facts. That we're not overreacting, we're not underreacting, we're
considering all the factors most relevant.''
</P>
<P>
   The most relevant factor is fear.
</P>
<P>
   Tim's friend had his hearing and received a long-term
