   &UR;  &LR;   &UR; LEHMAN COLLEGE ART GALLERY, &LR;  Bedford Park Boulevard West, at
Goulden Avenue, Kingsbridge, (718) 960-8731, Web site:
math240.lehman.cuny.edu/art/galleryinfo.html. ``Peter d'Agostino:
Interactivity and Intervention, 1978-1999'' and ``New Works: An
Exhibition of En Foco's 1998 Photography Award Winners.'' Through
May 15. Hours: Tuesdays through Saturdays, 10 a.m. to 4 p.m.
Information on En Foco: (718) 584-7718 or at www.nearbycafe.com.
 &UR;  &LR;   &UR; LONGWOOD ARTS GALLERY, &LR;  965 Longwood Ave., at Beck Street, South
Bronx, (718) 842-5659. ``Longwood Studio Fellowship Exhibit.''
Through June 26. Hours: Thursdays and Fridays, noon to 5 p.m.;
Saturdays, noon to 4 p.m.
</P>
