<P>
   &UR; CONFLICT IN THE BALKANS &LR;   &UR; (i) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   YUGOSLAVIA (Frankfurt, Germany) _ In what many describe as an
important diplomatic breakthrough, the world's biggest
industrialized nations and Russia agree on a plan they say could
end the conflict in Yugoslavia. By Kevin Cullen and Susan Milligan.
1250 words.
</P>
