Angeles, who is running for National Baptist Convention president
and has been a big supporter of Henry Lyons, the president who was
forced to resign because of financial irregularities and the fact
that his wife set fire to a beach house Lyons and his mistress
owned. (Perkes, Austin American-Statesman).
