<HEADER>
A7249 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-CREDIT-NYT &LR;      05-06 0029
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-CREDIT-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   CREDIT (New York) will not move in tonight's New York Times News
Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, May 6.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
