<HEADLINE>
TEAMS STILL LOOKING FOR MISSING, BUT NUMBER IS LOWER THAN EXPECTED
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By JACK DOUGLAS JR. 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   OKLAHOMA CITY _ Using listening devices and specially trained
dogs, rescue workers returned to obliterated neighborhoods on
